      "Determine base rate from age and gender",
      "Apply policy term factor",
      "Apply sum assured band factor", 
      "Apply occupation loading",
      "Apply health condition factor",
      "Apply tobacco usage factor",
      "Apply payment frequency factor",
      "Calculate applicable discounts",
      "Apply final premium adjustments"
